						></path></svg
					>
				</div>
				<h3
					class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-forest mb-3"
				>
					100% Grass-Fed
				</h3>
				<p class="text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
					Our Murray Greys graze naturally on Snake Valley
					pastures—never feedlots, never grain-finished, never
					hormones.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div
				class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl text-center border border-forest/5 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-forest/10"
			>
				<div
					class="w-16 h-16 bg-linear-to-br from-forest to-sage rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-5"
				>
					<svg class="w-8 h-8 fill-mint-light" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
						><path
							d="M18 18.5c.83 0 1.5-.67 1.5-1.5s-.67-1.5-1.5-1.5-1.5.67-1.5 1.5.67 1.5 1.5 1.5zM19.5 9.5l1.94 2.78.8-.21-1.64-2.36c-.24-.34-.61-.54-1-.57L15 9l-1.5-4.5H10V6h2.5l1.12 3.36L9 10.8l-.95-2.56L5.67 8l.52 1.45c.19.52.67.9 1.23.97L11 11v5.5l-3.78 1.03.04.47.17 1.1L11 18v.5c0 .83.67 1.5 1.5 1.5s1.5-.67 1.5-1.5V18l2.48-.68c.65-.17 1.15-.61 1.39-1.17l1.3-3.02L19.5 9.5zM17 5c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2s-.9-2-2-2-2 .9-2 2 .9 2 2 2z"
						></path></svg
					>
				</div>
				<h3
					class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-forest mb-3"
				>
					We Deliver Personally
				</h3>
				<p class="text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
					No couriers, no cold chain worries. We personally bring your
					box to your door across Ballarat and surrounds—free.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div
				class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl text-center border border-forest/5 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-forest/10"
			>
				<div
					class="w-16 h-16 bg-linear-to-br from-forest to-sage rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-5"
				>
					<svg class="w-8 h-8 fill-mint-light" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
						><path
							d="M12 3L1 9l4 2.18v6L12 21l7-3.82v-6l2-1.09V17h2V9L12 3zm6.82 6L12 12.72 5.18 9 12 5.28 18.82 9zM17 15.99l-5 2.73-5-2.73v-3.72L12 15l5-2.73v3.72z"
						></path></svg
					>
				</div>
				<h3
					class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-forest mb-3"
				>
					Know Your Farmer
				</h3>
				<p class="text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
					This is our land, our cattle, our family business. When you
					have questions, you're talking directly to us.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div
				class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl text-center border border-forest/5 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-forest/10"
			>
				<div
					class="w-16 h-16 bg-linear-to-br from-forest to-sage rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-5"
				>
					<svg class="w-8 h-8 fill-mint-light" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
						><path
							d="M11.8 10.9c-2.27-.59-3-1.2-3-2.15 0-1.09 1.01-1.85 2.7-1.85 1.78 0 2.44.85 2.5 2.1h2.21c-.07-1.72-1.12-3.3-3.21-3.81V3h-3v2.16c-1.94.42-3.5 1.68-3.5 3.61 0 2.31 1.91 3.46 4.7 4.13 2.5.6 3 1.48 3 2.41 0 .69-.49 1.79-2.7 1.79-2.06 0-2.87-.92-2.98-2.1h-2.2c.12 2.19 1.76 3.42 3.68 3.83V21h3v-2.15c1.95-.37 3.5-1.5 3.5-3.55 0-2.84-2.43-3.81-4.7-4.4z"
						></path></svg
					>
				</div>
				<h3
					class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-forest mb-3"
				>
					Skip the Markup
				</h3>
				<p class="text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
					Better beef for less money. Direct from paddock to your door
					means no supermarket margins.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

